# SECTION 4: DESCRIPTION
# ============================================
description:
  - "Spread the charm of Valentine’s Day and connect with your farm area in a way homeowners genuinely appreciate. These 6×9 real estate Valentine postcards feature eye-catching designs, warm messaging, and space for your branding so you stay top of mind during a season built around connection."
  - "Choose from professionally designed themes like Strawberry Milkshake recipes, elegant XO layouts, cheerful rainbow greetings, and classic hearts and floral styles that appeal to a wide audience. Our all-inclusive pricing covers printing, mailing, and postage, making it simple to launch a campaign without hidden costs."
  - "Add a home valuation QR code to generate instant seller leads and receive notifications the moment it’s scanned. Valentine postcards pair perfectly with just listed, just sold, and market update campaigns to create consistent visibility and long-term brand recognition."
  - "This is a simple way to reach your farm with something thoughtful instead of salesy. A well-timed Valentine campaign helps build familiarity, trust, and conversations that can turn into future listings."

