# ============================================
# SECTION 9: FAQs
# ============================================
faqs:
  - question: "Why should I use Valentine's Day postcards in my real estate marketing?"
    answer: "Valentine postcards create a friendly, personal touch that homeowners enjoy receiving. They build positive brand recognition without feeling like a hard sales pitch and help you stay top of mind."
  - question: "Can Valentine's postcards generate real estate leads?"
    answer: "Yes. You can add a QR code for automated home valuations. When homeowners scan it, you receive instant notifications and actionable seller leads."
  - question: "Can I customize the postcards with my branding?"
    answer: "Absolutely. You can add your logo, colors, headshot, and contact information using our online editor so every postcard reflects your brand."
  - question: "How do I know when my postcards are delivered?"
    answer: "Our mail tracking system shows when postcards arrive in mailboxes so you can plan follow-ups at the right time."
  - question: "Do you provide mailing lists for my campaign?"
    answer: "Yes. You can build targeted lists using our advanced list builder or upload your own mailing list to reach your farm or sphere of influence."
  - question: "Is there a minimum order quantity?"
    answer: "No. You can order as many or as few postcards as you need, making it easy to test campaigns or scale your marketing."
